<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/handlebars@latest/dist/handlebars.js"></script>

    <title>Home page</title>
</head>

<body>
    <h1 style="color: #5e9ca0;">E-Commerce API Routes</h1>
    <h2 style="color: #2e6c80;">User Authentication:</h2>
    <p>1. Register a user with:</p>
    <ul>
    <li>Method: GET</li>
    <li>Endpoint: <a href="/api/auth/register">/api/auth/register</a></li>
    <li>Body raw JSON:&nbsp;
    <ul>
    <li>name</li>
    <li>lastname</li>
    <li>email</li>
    <li>password</li>
    </ul>
    </li>
    </ul>
    <p>2. Request your auth token with:</p>
    <ul>
    <li>Method: GET</li>
    <li>Endpoint: <a href="/api/auth/register">/api/auth/login</a></li>
    <li>Body raw JSON:
    <ul>
    <li>email</li>
    <li>password</li>
    </ul>
    </li>
    </ul>
    <h2 style="color: #2e6c80;">Productos:</h2>
    <p>1. Get All Products:</p>
    <ul>
    <li>Method: GET</li>
    <li>Endpoint: <a href="/api/productos/">/api/productos</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p>2. Get Product By ID:</p>
    <ul>
    <li>Method: GET</li>
    <li>Endpoint: <a href="/api/productos/">/api/productos/:id</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p>3. Create Product:</p>
    <ul>
    <li>Method: POST</li>
    <li>Endpoint: <a href="/api/productos/">/api/productos</a></li>
    <li>Body raw JSON
    <ul>
    <li>title -&gt; String</li>
    <li>description -&gt; String</li>
    <li>code -&gt; String</li>
    <li>thumbnail -&gt; Image URL</li>
    <li>price -&gt; Number</li>
    <li>stock&nbsp; -&gt; Number</li>
    </ul>
    </li>
    </ul>
    <p>4. Delete Product:</p>
    <ul>
    <li>Method: DELETE</li>
    <li>Endpoint: <a href="/api/productos/">/api/productos/:id</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p>5. Edit Product:</p>
    <ul>
    <li>Method: PUT</li>
    <li>Endpoint: <a href="/api/productos/">/api/productos/:id</a></li>
    <li>Body raw JSON
    <ul>
    <li>title -&gt; String</li>
    <li>description -&gt; String</li>
    <li>code -&gt; String</li>
    <li>thumbnail -&gt; Image URL</li>
    <li>price -&gt; Number</li>
    <li>stock&nbsp; -&gt; Number</li>
    </ul>
    </li>
    </ul>
    <p>&nbsp;</p>
    <h2 style="color: #2e6c80;">Cart:</h2>
    <p>1. Get All Carts</p>
    <ul>
    <li>Method: GET</li>
    <li>Endpoint: <a href="/api/carritos">/api/carritos</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p>&nbsp;</p>
    <p>2. Get User Cart</p>
    <ul>
    <li>Method: GET</li>
    <li>Authentication: Bearer token</li>
    <li>Endpoint: <a href="/api/carritos/usercart">/api/carritos/usercart</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p>3. Get Cart by ID</p>
    <ul>
    <li>Method: GET</li>
    <li>Endpoint: <a href="/api/carritos/:id">/api/carritos/:id</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p>4. Add Cart to User</p>
    <ul>
    <li>Method: POST</li>
    <li>Authentication: Bearer token</li>
    <li>Endpoint: <a href="/api/carritos">/api/carritos</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p>5. Remove Product from Cart</p>
    <ul>
    <li>Method: Delete</li>
    <li>Authentication: Bearer token</li>
    <li>Endpoint: <a href="/api/carritos/usercart/productos/:productId">/api/carritos/usercart/productos/:productId</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p>&nbsp;</p>
    <p>6. Delete cart</p>
    <ul>
    <li>Method: Delete</li>
    <li>Authentication: Bearer token</li>
    <li>Endpoint: <a href="/api/carritos/usercart/">/api/carritos/usercart/</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p>&nbsp;</p>
    <p>7. BUY</p>
    <ul>
    <li>Method: POST</li>
    <li>Authentication: Bearer token</li>
    <li>Endpoint: <a href="/api/carritos/usercart/buy">/api/carritos/usercart/buy</a></li>
    </ul>
</body>

</html>